Package: contrastable
Type: Package
Title: Tidy contrast coding utilities
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Thomas Sostarics
Maintainer: Thomas Sostarics <tsostarics@gmail.com>
Description: A package to easily set contrasts for factor variables
    in regression analyses. Provide common and consistent scheme
    names to use for contrast coding that "just works."
